➜徐以成（福建）：诗二首
http://www.sohu.com/a/419879678_100115135	37121
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗二首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/徐以成</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200921/d4684bb05ecf44468ffb7a591035ee41.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1.春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳絮纷飞万缕丝，八方绿暖燕归时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旧寒化雨无残迹，灵气生晖有自知。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就近芳菲花草醉，散开胸臆胆肝痴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三春神韵为何物？似梦如图又若诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200921/db22dfe6b2934da486209d174f4c0195.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2.春游</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春雨霖铃好踏青，和风送暖气清明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莺歌燕舞枝头闹，花柳芳菲满地菁。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
